      <h2>How your data will be used</h2>

      <p>Continuum Design will only ask for a minimal amount of data to contact you. This may include your name, email address, and/or a telephone number. Your data will be used to answer questions or requests for work submitted. Additionally, your data may be used to respond to emails regarding sales, general information, or security.</p>

      <h2>Data retention policy</h2>

      <p>All information submitted through the contact form older than thirty (30) days will be deleted. Direct email conversations older than the previous calendar year will be archived offline.</p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>

